{"tid":475964,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[煮食台] 想整tiramisu 求交流","createTime":"2017-11-21T14:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T11:20:50.000Z","uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"71bcf1e9f43c9da36616995e01831450487bddb9","tid":475964,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:49:46.000Z","msg":"十年前整過一排蛋榚 放低晒<br />\n最近想整tiramisu 比個素食朋友<br />\n求一個好嘅食譜 <br />\n同買材料地點 以前好似過海去二德惠<br />\n依家有咩地方多選擇<br />\n打蛋機比人一借無回頭要買過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4945dd52bdc85671d3ba513ad3af54fbf69297f","tid":475964,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f634ed989272a232afd8494d6581057cc39e93","tid":475964,"uid":75419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"旺角有間野有唔同package包哂用具材料..2手fingfing 行入去就得..應該岩你..x假期早排日日做廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757b1c008ac19711eda52b04d8c630354f7eb80f","tid":475964,"uid":10788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>旺角有間野有唔同package包哂用具材料..2手fingfing 行入去就得..應該岩你..x假期早排日日做廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌新假期老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我要自己整唔要預拌粉<br />\n一來難食 二來通常有魚膠粉 朋友唔食得<br />\n基本工具我有 餅模 蛋糕刮 磅 量匙 嗰啲"},{"pid":"75c502134dffeb9ec7d9cb8b33d71e6927e70d30","tid":475964,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T01:25:56.000Z","msg":"食素無得用生雞蛋唔啱佢食"},{"pid":"553e14a90f7c219e0d615aad0a49d38ab0c01002","tid":475964,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T01:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食素無得用生雞蛋唔啱佢食</blockquote><br />\n雞蛋同牛奶佢都食嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9ee30a9b3c202703401407c26d2d8d7969f145","tid":475964,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T06:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd8907b0355a39364b7cdcb22205e9ae1d542b1","tid":475964,"uid":42318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:33:49.000Z","msg":"Google 烘焙店+地區都有堆result啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d62a26f618048355c65359f0d9c078f41769486","tid":475964,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"其實如果你朋友食蛋奶素嘅話好似冇乜需要改食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗最大分別應該都係食材質素<br />\n買隻靚啲滑啲香啲嘅cream cheese已經好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴返頭盔先<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699deed71cda31b70fffd557303cc12e9734fd73","tid":475964,"uid":57148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:57:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cucchiaio.it/ricetta/ricetta-tiramisu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cucchiaio.it%2Fricetta%2Fricetta-tiramisu%2F&d=xrBgDHWVdE9St%2FhBMWi%2BGDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e277e267\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cucchiaio.it/ricetta/ricetta-tiramisu/</a><br />\n<br />\nCucchiaio d'Argento 係意大利一本幾出名既cookbook黎<br />\n唔識意大利文唔緊要 因為有圖+google translate"},{"pid":"d88140b7e7bd7b1fb7ccbaf0b29bd4a39602f60b","tid":475964,"uid":61267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"小白原來有煮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362f3740b48598349ed1c7c224f8b03e199e3e2e","tid":475964,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.cucchiaio.it/ricetta/ricetta-tiramisu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cucchiaio.it%2Fricetta%2Fricetta-tiramisu%2F&d=xrBgDHWVdE9St%2FhBMWi%2BGDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e277e267\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cucchiaio.it/ricetta/ricetta-tiramisu/</a><br />\n<br />\nCucchiaio d'Argento 係意大利一本幾出名既cookbook黎<br />\n唔識意大利文唔緊要 因為有圖+google translate</blockquote><br />\n哇 我除左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都唔知可以講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝巴打<br />\n放假去執貨"},{"pid":"5fda3df818ae2b7571ae7dad6f1409d2e0de25ed","tid":475964,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小白原來有煮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地share account <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢本身都有煮野"},{"pid":"6ea8f048b93b6c0220bb91d40325392c10ffed73","tid":475964,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實如果你朋友食蛋奶素嘅話好似冇乜需要改食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗最大分別應該都係食材質素<br />\n買隻靚啲滑啲香啲嘅cream cheese已經好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴返頭盔先<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多食譜都唔正宗 同會落魚膠粉令個蛋榚企身<br />\n魚膠粉係動物蛋白黎㗎"},{"pid":"26ac5f03421f20cb243a85f176790bf06a98b4fc","tid":475964,"uid":10788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:52:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實如果你朋友食蛋奶素嘅話好似冇乜需要改食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗最大分別應該都係食材質素<br />\n買隻靚啲滑啲香啲嘅cream cheese已經好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戴返頭盔先<br />\n有錯請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多食譜都唔正宗 同會落魚膠粉令個蛋榚企身<br />\n魚膠粉係動物蛋白黎㗎</blockquote><br />\n同埋無記錯嘅話tiramisu 係無cream cheese <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c0eb27125441bf15fa0d57c47ce581bbb56e6a","tid":475964,"uid":61267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小白原來有煮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地share account <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢本身都有煮野</blockquote><br />\n女女女"},{"pid":"51962f4f1848d46693dbaab2a1625d8419a0c276","tid":475964,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小白原來有煮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地share account <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢本身都有煮野</blockquote><br />\n女女女</blockquote><br />\nSorry 我有J㗎"},{"pid":"6b124bd61dbea3351229c71afbbaa3e9f4c7dfd4","tid":475964,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n同埋無記錯嘅話tiramisu 係無cream cheese <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我未整過有魚膠粉嘅食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係叫Mascarpone cheese？<br />\n我認個產品樣sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23fcfcdede4ed60690721d98c27f2f33faef9059","tid":475964,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T02:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n同埋無記錯嘅話tiramisu 係無cream cheese <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我未整過有魚膠粉嘅食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係叫Mascarpone cheese？<br />\n我認個產品樣sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傳統用Mascarpone cheese<br />\n用cream cheese會有陣酸味同硬身啲<br />\n不過冇Mascarpone可以用cream cheese + whipping cream + 砂糖"},{"pid":"aa8815e1bb66f75ade6a5ff00ed71f3fdf691317","tid":475964,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T04:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n同埋無記錯嘅話tiramisu 係無cream cheese <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我未整過有魚膠粉嘅食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係叫Mascarpone cheese？<br />\n我認個產品樣sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傳統用Mascarpone cheese<br />\n用cream cheese會有陣酸味同硬身啲<br />\n不過冇Mascarpone可以用cream cheese + whipping cream + 砂糖</blockquote><br />\n應該會跟上面個巴打嘅食譜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下落蛋白霜同cream 係味道上分別係咩？<br />\n因為兩樣野分別都幾大 不過有食譜會用cream 有啲用蛋白霜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d214e608ccab8b5287c25b445df4ce370b748808","tid":475964,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n同埋無記錯嘅話tiramisu 係無cream cheese <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我未整過有魚膠粉嘅食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係叫Mascarpone cheese？<br />\n我認個產品樣sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傳統用Mascarpone cheese<br />\n用cream cheese會有陣酸味同硬身啲<br />\n不過冇Mascarpone可以用cream cheese + whipping cream + 砂糖</blockquote><br />\n應該會跟上面個巴打嘅食譜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下落蛋白霜同cream 係味道上分別係咩？<br />\n因為兩樣野分別都幾大 不過有食譜會用cream 有啲用蛋白霜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTiramisu用蛋白霜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蛋白霜好少聽到話生食, 頂多係梳乎厘咁唔焗透<br />\n蛋糕搽面, 唧花, 或者唔焗嘅甜品係用whipping cream<br />\n牛奶整嘅whipping cream好濃奶味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />植物性忌廉味道淡同感覺唔係好自然, 而且本身已經落咗糖, 成件甜品落幾多糖會難計啲<br />\n生蛋白就未食過, 但係就咁聞都好腥吓,<br />\n就咁打成蛋白霜生食應該唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外Bosch有隻手提打蛋機個底可以裝枝攪拌棒變食物處理機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7287041bc7a52c8839c00e222a7a1cd1a3d13f","tid":475964,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n同埋無記錯嘅話tiramisu 係無cream cheese <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我未整過有魚膠粉嘅食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係叫Mascarpone cheese？<br />\n我認個產品樣sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傳統用Mascarpone cheese<br />\n用cream cheese會有陣酸味同硬身啲<br />\n不過冇Mascarpone可以用cream cheese + whipping cream + 砂糖</blockquote><br />\n應該會跟上面個巴打嘅食譜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下落蛋白霜同cream 係味道上分別係咩？<br />\n因為兩樣野分別都幾大 不過有食譜會用cream 有啲用蛋白霜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTiramisu用蛋白霜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蛋白霜好少聽到話生食, 頂多係梳乎厘咁唔焗透<br />\n蛋糕搽面, 唧花, 或者唔焗嘅甜品係用whipping cream<br />\n牛奶整嘅whipping cream好濃奶味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />植物性忌廉味道淡同感覺唔係好自然, 而且本身已經落咗糖, 成件甜品落幾多糖會難計啲<br />\n生蛋白就未食過, 但係就咁聞都好腥吓,<br />\n就咁打成蛋白霜生食應該唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外Bosch有隻手提打蛋機個底可以裝枝攪拌棒變食物處理機<img